KSrelief distributed more than 89 tons of food baskets to families in Al-Mahra governorate, benefiting more than 5,000 individuals.
The assistance is part of a project to distribute more than 192,000 food baskets weighing more than 20,000 tons to needy and affected families in 15 Yemeni governorates.